·

THE SCOPE, NATURE OR IMPACT OF ACQUISITION OR DISPOSITION ACTIVITY, SUCH AS AVIALL, AND INVESTMENT IN ANY JOINT VENTURES INCLUDING SEA LAUNCH AND UNITED LAUNCH ALLIANCE,

