LOWER IDS EARNINGS REFLECTING A $569 MILLION NET GAIN ON THE SALE OF OUR ROCKETDYNE BUSINESS IN 2005 AND $770 MILLION OF CHARGES ON THE AIRBORNE EARLY WARNING & CONTROL (AEW&C) DEVELOPMENT PROGRAM IN 2006 PARTIALLY OFFSET BY IMPROVED MARGINS

