END OF THE REPORTING PERIOD. ACCORDINGLY, EARNINGS FROM OPERATIONS INCLUDED $746 MILLION, $1,225 MILLION AND $335 MILLION OF PENSION EXPENSE IN 2006, 2005, AND 2004,

