INC. (AVIALL), NET OF $42 MILLION OF CASH ACQUIRED, AND $458 MILLION OF ASSUMED DEBT, IN AN ALL-CASH MERGER. THE ASSUMED DEBT WAS SUBSEQUENTLY REPAID ON THE ACQUISITION CLOSING DATE. IN 2005, WE RECEIVED PROCEEDS OF $1,676 MILLION, PRIMARILY FROM

THE DISPOSITION OF OUR COMMERCIAL AIRPLANES

