INSTRUMENTS (U.S. DOLLAR DEBT OBLIGATIONS OF THE UNITED STATES TREASURY, OTHER GOVERNMENT AGENCIES, CORPORATIONS, MORTGAGE-BACKED AND ASSET-BACKED SECURITIES). AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2006, OUR EXTERNALLY MANAGED PORTFOLIO OF INVESTMENT GRADE FIXED

