AVERAGE PRICE OF $63.60 AND $51.09 IN OUR OPEN MARKET SHARE REPURCHASE PROGRAM, AND 33,660 SHARES AND 50,657 SHARES WERE REPURCHASED IN STOCK SWAPS.

