THE BALANCE OF DEFERRED PRODUCTION COSTS AND UNAMORTIZED TOOLING RELATED TO COMMERCIAL AIRCRAFT PROGRAMS, EXCEPT THE 777 PROGRAM, WAS INSIGNIFICANT RELATIVE TO THE PROGRAMS BALANCE-TO-GO ESTIMATES. AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2006 AND 2005, ALL

