THE NEXT TWELVE MONTHS. ACCOUNTS PAYABLE INCLUDED $335 AND $204 AT DECEMBER 31, 2006 AND 2005, ATTRIBUTABLE TO CHECKS WRITTEN BUT NOT YET CLEARED BY THE BANK.

