RELATED TO THE U.S. GOVERNMENT. OF THE $8,204 OF AIRCRAFT CUSTOMER FINANCING, $7,712 RELATED TO CUSTOMERS WE BELIEVE HAVE LESS THAN INVESTMENT-GRADE CREDIT. AIRTRAN AIRWAYS, AMR, UNITED AIRLINES AND MIDWEST AIRLINES INC. WERE ASSOCIATED WITH 19%,

14% 9% AND 8%, RESPECTIVELY, OF OUR AIRCRAFT FINANCING PORTFOLIO. FINANCING FOR AIRCRAFT IS COLLATERALIZED BY SECURITY IN THE RELATED ASSET. AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2006, THERE WAS $10,164 OF FINANCING COMMITMENTS RELATED TO AIRCRAFT ON ORDER

INCLUDING OPTIONS DESCRIBED IN NOTE 23, OF WHICH $8,356 RELATED TO CUSTOMERS WE BELIEVE HAVE LESS THAN INVESTMENT-GRADE CREDIT.

OTHER RISK

