CONSIDERED PROBABLE, SHOULD WE INCUR REMEDIATION CHARGES AT THE HIGH LEVEL OF THE RANGE OF POTENTIAL EXPOSURE, THE ADDITIONAL CHARGES WOULD BE LESS THAN 2% OF HISTORICAL ANNUAL REVENUES.

