FINANCIAL STATEMENT SCHEDULE AS OF AND FOR THE YEAR ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2006 OF THE COMPANY AND OUR REPORT DATED FEBRUARY 15, 2007 EXPRESSED AN UNQUALIFIED OPINION ON THOSE FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND FINANCIAL STATEMENT SCHEDULE AND INCLUDED

