EMPLOYEES, INCLUDING OUR CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER (CEO), (COLLECTIVELY, THE CODES OF CONDUCT). THE CODES OF CONDUCT ARE POSTED ON OUR WEBSITE, WWW.BOEING.COM. WE INTEND TO DISCLOSE ON OUR WEBSITE ANY AMENDMENTS TO, OR WAIVERS OF, THE

CODES OF CONDUCT COVERING OUR CEO, CFO AND/OR CONTROLLER PROMPTLY FOLLOWING THE DATE OF SUCH AMENDMENTS OR WAIVERS. A COPY OF THE CODES OF CONDUCT MAY BE OBTAINED UPON REQUEST, WITHOUT CHARGE, BY CONTACTING OUR OFFICE OF INTERNAL GOVERNANCE AT

